data.description: This property is the perfect home to get away and enjoy the outdoors. Come out and see the beautiful mountain views and countryside settings this house has to offer!Seller is motivated and willing to work with buyers. This home located in the middle of Rutledge offering scenic views and a quiet, almost one acre lot that has a lot of potential and would be the ideal home for anyone looking for plenty of storage, privacy and room!
